Heavenly youth cast into exile by cruel fate, granting
peace unto Catkind. Strong vs Red/Alien/Zombie/Relics,
Explosions 100% Freeze, plus Wave Shield.

name: Bowler Cat
Dodgeballer Cat
desc:
Pro indoor sportscat knocking all rivals to the gutter
with polished throws of a hefty ball. Sage Slayer,
Slows Aku/Traitless, with chance of Mini-Wave.

Despite unusual form, his unmatched accuracy
is feared by all in the local league. Sage Slayer,
Slows Aku/Traitless, with chance of Mini-Wave.

name: Mamoluga
Mamolan Pasalan
desc:
Not sure if this is a Cat...
There's just something about
that stout torso...

Why does it cover its eyes? Best not think about it.
Seems like this one is a Conjurer
whose Area Attacks can Weaken enemies.
Spirit: Weakens enemies.

name: Koneko
Superstar Koneko
desc:
Tomboyish Cat dreaming of being an idol adored by
crowds of fans. Performs her heart out on stage,
amassing more and more fans by the day.

An unexpected breakthrough hit pushed Koneko
onto the path of becoming a star. Gives it all for her
fans with passionate singing to show her gratitude.

name: Killer Gross Cat
True Killer Gross Cat
desc:
A Gross Cat with its feral side unleashed.
Strikes enemies at distance with long, mighty legs.
Costs a bit extra to recruit to fight for you.

Its feral side has completely overwhelmed it.
Takes pride in the attack range of his long legs.
Single enemy attacks have exceptional power and range.

name: The Amazing Catman
Illusionist Catman
desc:
Clad in white garb, delights children with magic.
Instantly teleports to fans to give autographs.
Area attack deals Massive damage to Red/Floating.

Clad in jet black, mystifies ladies with illusory magic.
Returns burgled goods to their rightful owners.
Area attack deals Massive damage to Red/Angels.

name: Netherworld Nymph Lunacia
Death's Daughter Lunacia
desc:
Another avatar of mercy guiding forlorn Cats to 
redemption. Strong vs. and Weakens Floating/Angels/
Aku/Traitless. Omnistrikes cause Explosions. Counters Surges.

Devoted to the salvation of all others, even at the cost of 
her own. Strong vs. and Weakens Floating/Angels/Aku/
Traitless. Omnistrikes cause Explosions. Counters Surges.

name: Baki Hanma
Baki Hanma CC
desc:
Joining from Baki! Young Champion of the 
Underground Arena who has won many fierce
battles. May Knockback Aku and Pierce Shields.

Joining from Baki! Desires strength to 
defeat his father Yujiro Hanma.
May Knockback Aku and Pierce Shields.

name: Retsu Kaioh
Retsu Kaioh CC
desc:
Fighter who gained the title of Kaioh, the highest 
mark in Chinese martial arts. Behemoth Slayer, 
Strong vs. and may Freeze Red and Aliens.

Joining from Baki! The greatest genius in the 
4000-year history of Chinese martial arts pugilists.
Strong vs. and may Freeze Red and Aliens.

name: Kaoru Hanayama
Kaoru Hanayama CC
desc:
The second head of the Hanayama Group,
known as Japan's greatest brawler. Tough vs. and
deals Massive damage to Aku. Pierces Shields.

Takes pride in his above-average grip strength. 
Fisticuffs is his passion. Tough vs. and
deals Massive damage to Aku. Pierces Shields.

name: Katsumi Orochi
Katsumi Orochi CC
desc:
Adopted son of Doppo Orochi who inherited Shinshinkai 
as its young leader. Breaks Barriers and deals
Massive damage to Red and Aliens with area attacks!

Lethal weapon of the karate world with apex strength 
and ability. Breaks Barriers and deals Massive
damage to Red and Aliens with area attacks!

name: Jack Hammer
Jack Hammer CC
desc:
Baki's half-brother who'll do whatever it takes to 
gain strength. Metal Killer with 100% chance to 
Weaken Zombies and Metal enemies!

His oppressive bite strength can crush even 
a coconut. Metal Killer with 100% chance to
Weaken Zombies and Metal enemies!

name: Ogre Cat
Ogre Cat Face
desc:
Cat that fights to become the strongest thing alive. 
Reads encyclopedias to know its rival's weaknesses.
May Knockback and Slow Aliens.

Cat fighting to be the strongest thing alive. Intimidates
foes with its Cat Face back muscles to avoid combat.
May Knockback and Slow Aliens.

name: Li'l Baki
Li'l Baki CC
desc:
Joining from Baki! Young fighter who aims to challenge
their father, known as "the strongest thing alive."
Has the Metal Killer ability.

Joining from Baki! Overcame many trials, wearing the
scars of many past battles like medals.
Has the Metal Killer ability.

name: Baki Cat
Baki Cat CC
desc:
Cat who trains day and night to become a fighter. 
Currently undefeated in image training.
Omnistrikes may Knockback Aliens.

Cat training to refine its rushing technique. 
Home life is a series of sharp-tongued spats.
Omnistrikes may Knockback Aliens.

name: Kaioh Cat
Kaioh Cat CC
desc:
Cat who titled themselves the 2nd strongest master of 
Chinese Kenpo. Can crush a polished mud ball in one 
strike. Area atk. deals Massive damage to Floating/Black.

Cat training to excel at Chinese martial arts. After much 
study, can now walk across 6 inches of water.
Area atk. deals Massive damage to Floating/Black.

name: Doppo Cat
Doppo Cat CC
desc:
Cat aiming to head the Shinshinkai. Right eye taken 
from a beggar is receiving medical care. May Freeze
Red enemies with Long-range Area attacks.

Cat who idolizes a famed fighter who fells tigers 
barehanded. Spins wild yarns about fights it had no part
in. Long-range Area attacks May Freeze Red enemies.

name: Mighty Morta-Loncha
Grandiose Gunhauzer
desc:
Experimental weapon developed to oppose an ancient
empire. Launches attacks in a parabolic arc. Conjurer,
may Freeze Zombies and Aku with Explosion attacks.

Developed as a last resort against an ancient army. 
Repels foes with optimized cannonballs. Conjurer,
may Freeze Zombies/Aku with Explosion attacks.
Spirit: Has the Zombie Killer and Soulstrike abilities.

name: Master of Logic Newton
Master of Logic Mewton
desc:
Joined the Cat Army to solve the mysteries surrounding
Cats and their lack of adherence to logic. Conjurer, Sage
Slayer, Slows Red/Floating, unleashes Mini-Waves.

Discovered the Law of Attraction to Cats after field
research with the Cat Army. Conjurer, Sage Slayer,
Slows Red/Floating, unleashes Mini-Waves.
Spirit: Deals Knockback to enemies.

name: Sonic
Sonic & Cat
desc:
Joining from Sonic the Hedgehog thanks to divine power!
Cool and spiky hedgehog who runs at supersonic speed.
100% Knockback/Slow/Massive damage to Angels.

Joining from Sonic the Hedgehog thanks to divine power!
Wouldn't complain if you made me look more handsome...
100% Knockback/Slow/Massive damage to Angels.

name: Tails
Tails & Cat
desc:
Joining from Sonic the Hedgehog thanks to divine power!
Kind-hearted young fox with a pair of tails.
May afflict Red/Aliens with debuffs, causes Explosions.

Joining from Sonic the Hedgehog thanks to divine power!
Divine power... I wonder how it works...
May afflict Red/Aliens with debuffs, causes Explosions.

name: Knuckles
Knuckles & Cat
desc:
Joining from Sonic the Hedgehog thanks to divine power!
One punch from this echidna can pulverize a boulder.
Strong vs. Red and Zombies.

Joining from Sonic the Hedgehog thanks to divine power!
Heh! I'll take on any Cat that comes my way!
Strong vs. Red and Zombies.

name: Shadow
Shadow & Cat
desc:
Joining from Sonic the Hedgehog thanks to divine power!
Black hedgehog who's almost like Sonic's double!
Deals Massive damage to Black and Zombies.

Joining from Sonic the Hedgehog thanks to divine power!
Who's the fake here? Let's see how alike we really are.
Deals Massive damage to Black and Zombies.

name: Sonic Cat
Sonic Cat CC
desc:
Cat who adores a supersonic hedgehog.
Has to take medicine for motion sickness due to a weak inner ear.
Deals Massive damage to Aliens.

Cat who underwent surgery in the hope of developing
slightly faster legs. (Did not translate to a speed increase.)
Tough vs Aliens.

name: Tails Cat
Tails Cat CC
desc:
Cat who adores a two-tailed flying fox. Currently on a
diet to achieve a flying altitude higher than 0 feet.
May Slow Angels.

Cat who always ends up with spare parts
after reassembling the machines they tinker with.
100% chance to Slow Angels.

name: Shadow Cat
Shadow Cat CC
desc:
Cat who adores a specific ultimate lifeform.
Regularly dyes their fur black to emulate their hero.
Tough vs Metal.

Cat who uses a jewel's power to warp space-time to
such a degree that the current year is now unknown.
Tough vs Metal.

name: Agent Staal
Edgemaster Staal
desc:
Mercenary who sold out his allies for fortune and power.
His godlike bladework is Strong vs Metal/Zombies/Aku.
May Slow and unleash Mini-Waves.

Obtained untold power through cybernetic implants.
This combination of man and machine is Strong vs
Metal/Zombies/Aku, may Slow, unleashes Mini-Waves.

name: Victorious Skanda
Zeta Skanda
desc:
One of the Eight Generals of the Pure Realm.
A Conjurer and Sage Slayer who unleashes Waves
that always Weaken Red, Angel and Alien enemies.

His heavenly blade cuts down demons with panache.
A Conjurer and Sage Slayer who unleashes Waves
that always Weaken Red, Angel and Alien enemies.
Spirit: Freezes enemies.

name: Tasmanian Giant Crab
Tasmanian Giant Crab CC
desc:
Dropping in from "Survive! Mola Mola!"
World's largest crab... and dangerously tasty.
Chance to Break Barriers

Dropping in from "Survive! Mola Mola!"
One hit from that sharp right claw and
you're out! Chance to Break Barriers

name: Mass Production EVA
Mass Production EVA-Cat
desc:
Recruited from EVANGELION!
Produced by SEELE to complete the Human
Instrumentality Project. May Freeze Traitless/Angels.

Cat-made replica of the Mass Production EVA unit.
Developed to complete the Human Catification Project.
May Freeze Traitless/Angels.

name: Moonshade Kaworu
Moon Disciple Kaworu
desc:
Came from the moon to complete his mission.
Conjurer, Sage Slayer, deals Insane damage to Traitless
and may deal Knockback with long-range area attacks.

In an eternal cycle of striving for a friend's happiness.
Conjurer, Sage Slayer, deals Insane damage to Traitless
and may deal Knockback with long-range area attacks.
Spirit: Weakens and Slows enemies.

name: Komori
Moririn
desc:
Tree spirit from the far reaches of space who 
resurrects fallen stars with the power of nature. 
May Curse Black and Alien enemies.

Wields mastery over all plant life, willing nature to 
flourish wildly to Break Barriers. Colossus/Behemoth
Slayer, Conjurer. Tough vs Black/Aliens, 100% Curse.
Spirit: Weakens enemies.

name: Carpenter Cat
Rapper Cat
desc:
Diligent worker who always keeps Safety First in mind.
A virtuoso creating pulse-pounding beats with rhythmic 
hammering. Sage Slayer, Tough vs Red/Floating.

Whether hammering nails or spitting rhymes with mic in
hand, a steady beat is the key to incredible productivity.
Sage Slayer, Tough vs Red/Floating.

name: Seaside Pegasa
Seaside Pegasa v
desc:
Granted her first ever summer vacation, this young 
noble is filled with joy at the sight of the ocean. Conjurer,
Weakens Traitless and Black, unleashes Mini-Waves.

The dazzling grin on her face is an inspiration to the kids
who cheer her on from the seashore. Conjurer, 
Weakens Traitless and Black, unleashes Mini-Waves.
Spirit: Slows enemies.

name: Consultant Cat
Business Partner Cat
desc:
The savior of countless business ventures, they have no
equal when it comes to bringing profit and success to a 
company. Metal Killer, may Slow Metal enemies.

Has no equal when it comes to maximizing profit and 
minimizing losses by any means necessary.
Metal Killer, may Slow Metal enemies.

name: Sorceress Sidmi
Flame Mage Sidmi
desc:
Powerful magician from the astral planes. Uses magic to
maintain youthful looks at 300 years old. Sage Slayer, 
Conjurer, Tough vs. and may Slow Red/Floating.

Practiced magician who flies into a fiery rage when 
treated as a child (or an old woman.) Sage Slayer, 
Conjurer, Tough vs. and may Slow Red/Floating.
Spirit: Weakens enemies.

name: Cammy
Cammy CC
desc:
Joining from Street Fighter 6! Member of 
spec-ops group Delta Red. Deals Insane
damage to Aliens, may Dodge attacks.

Joining from Street Fighter 6! Punts foes into 
the air with her Cannon Spike. Deals Insane
damage to Aliens, may Dodge attacks.

name: Juri
Juri CC
desc:
Joining from Street Fighter 6! Delights in
others' suffering. Colossus/Behemoth Slayer
Strong vs. Angels/Floating, inflicts debuffs.

Joining from Street Fighter 6! Beats down foes
with Tensenrin. Colossus/Behemoth Slayer
Strong vs. Angels/Floating, inflicts debuffs.

name: Zangief Cat
Zangief Cat CC
desc:
Believes muscles reign supreme. Grows hair
in balding spots thanks to self-development.
Massive damage to Floating, may deal a Savage Blow.

Attained a pro-wrestler body akin to steel. Too
busy training to gain any real-world experience.
Massive damage to Floating, may Savage Blow.

name: Jamie Cat
Jamie Cat CC
desc:
Adores a Chinatown user of the drunken fist.
Everything tastes better coming from its gourd.
Strong vs. Aku, stronger after taking damage!

Only planned to fake being drunk, but ended up
drinking too much. Why is his hair so messy?
Strong vs. Aku, stronger after taking damage!

name: Raclesa the Lioness
Raclesa Σ
desc:
Mightiest woman of the academy who wrestles
weaklings less fit than her into submission.
Strong vs. Floating, Omnistrikes 100% Slow

The fierce aura of the galaxy's most swole 
woman has inspired legions of gal devotees.
Strong vs. Floating, Omnistrikes 100% Slow
